ENTRY       EC 2.4.1.211                Enzyme
NAME        1,3-beta-galactosyl-N-acetylhexosamine phosphorylase;
            lacto-N-biose phosphorylase;
            LNBP;
            galacto-N-biose phosphorylase
CLASS       Transferases;
            Glycosyltransferases;
            Hexosyltransferases
SYSNAME     beta-D-galactopyranosyl-(1->3)-N-acetyl-D-hexosamine:phosphate galactosyltransferase
REACTION    beta-D-galactopyranosyl-(1->3)-N-acetyl-D-glucosamine + phosphate = alpha-D-galactopyranose 1-phosphate + N-acetyl-D-glucosamine [RN:R05326 R06057]
ALL_REAC    R05326 R06057(G)
SUBSTRATE   beta-D-galactopyranosyl-(1->3)-N-acetyl-D-glucosamine [CPD:C06372];
            phosphate [CPD:C00009]
PRODUCT     alpha-D-galactopyranose 1-phosphate [CPD:C00446];
            N-acetyl-D-glucosamine [CPD:C00140]
COMMENT     Reaction also occurs with beta-D-galactopyranosyl-(1->3)-N-acetyl-D-galactosamine as the substrate, giving N-acetyl-D-galactosamine as the product.
